Use Case 1: Instant PRD Summary
Scenario:
A PM uploads a 20-page PRD.
AI Output:
•	TL;DR summary 
•	Key features 
•	Risks 
 Impact: Saves hours of reading time

 Use Case 2: Requirement Extraction
Input:
•	Meeting notes / research document 
Output:
•	Functional requirements 
•	User stories 
•	Prioritized features 
 Impact: Eliminates manual documentation

Use Case 3: Product Q&A Assistant
Scenario:
Engineer asks:
“What are the checkout flow requirements?”
AI Response:
•	Instant answer from PRD 
Impact: Reduces PM interruptions

 Use Case 4: Gap Detection
Scenario:
AI analyzes PRD and flags:
•	Missing success metrics 
•	Edge cases not covered 
•	Undefined risks 
 Impact: Prevents product failures

